               <msContents>
                  <summary>Homiliary in Honor of the Archangel Michael, ድርሳነ፡ ሚካኤል፡, Image of Michael, መልክአ፡ ሚካኤል፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from = "1r" to = "92v"/>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                    <incipit xml:lang = "gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡...ነጽሩ፡ አኃውየ፡ ፍቁራንየ፡ ዕበዩ፡ ወመንክሮ፡ ዘገብረ፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ሚካኤል፡ ለእለ፡ ይስእልዎ፡ በጽሒቅ፡...መፍትው፡ ከመ፡ ንግበር፡ ተዝካሮ፡</incipit>

                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                       <locus from = "4r" to = "14v"/>
                        <title><foreign xml:lang = "gez">ኅዳር፡</foreign></title>

                          <msItem xml:id = "ms_i1.1.1">
                            <title>Homily</title>
                            <note>Author not given</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                              <locus from ="4r" to = "9r"/> and <locus from = "10r" to = "13r"/>
                               በስመ፡ አብ፡...[ጳጳ]ሳት፡ ዘለእስክንድርያ፡ ዘበዓለ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ያርእየነ፡ ኀይለ፡ ወክብረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡...አውሎግሶን፡ ዐቢይ፡ በዓል፡ ፍቁራንየ፡ ንዑ፡ ንትጋባዕ፡...
                             </incipit>
                           </msItem>
                           <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1.2">
                             <title>Synaxary entry: the Archangel’s mission to Joshua son of Nun</title>
                             <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                               <locus from = "9v"/>ወበዛቲ፡ ዕለት፡ ተዝካረ፡ በዓሉ፡ ለመልአክ፡ ክቡር፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ሚካኤል፡...ዘርእዮ፡ ኢያሱ፡ ወልደ፡ ነዌ፡ በአምሳለ፡ ሐራሁ፡ ለንጉሥ፡...
                             </incipit>
                           </msItem>
                           <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1.3">
                             <title>Greeting to the Archangel</title>
                             <note>incomplete at the end</note>
                             <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                               <locus from = "9v"/>ሰላም፡ ለአስተርእዮትከ፡ ውስተ፡ ደብረ፡ ማሕው፡ ዮም፡
                             </incipit>
                           </msItem>
                           <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1.4">
                             <title>Miracle, introduction</title>
                             <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                               <locus from = "13r" to = "14v"/>በስመ፡ አብ፡...ንወጥን፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚብሔር፡ ጽሒፈ፡ ተአምሪሁ፡...ይቤ፡ ዐቢይ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወጥቀ፡ ልዑል፡ ዲበ፡ ኵሉ፡ ፍጥረት፡...
                             </incipit>
                           </msItem>
                           <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1.5">
                             <title>Text of the miracle: how the Archangel rescued the people whose boat was troubled by high wind</title>
                             <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                               <locus from = "14r"/>ተአምሪሁ፡...እከሥት፡ በምሳ[ሌ]፡ አፉየ፡ ወእንበብ፡ ኅቡዓተ፡ ዘእምትካት፡...
                             </incipit>
                           </msItem>
                         </msItem>

                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                       <locus from = "14v" to = "20v"/>
                       <title><foreign xml:lang = "gez">ታኅሣሥ፡</foreign></title>

                          <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.1">
                            <title>Homily</title>
                            <note>Author not given</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                              <locus from = "14v" to = "20r"/>
                              በስመ፡ አብ፡...እምጳጳሳት፡ ዘደረሰ፡ በእንተ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ዘይትነበብ፡ አመ፡ ፲ወ፪ለወርኃ፡ ታኅሣሥ፡ በሰላመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አሜን። መፍትው፡ ለነ፡ ፍቁራንየ፡ ንዘከር፡ ዕበዮ፡ ለአብ፡ ኂሩቶ፡ ለወልድ፡ ወጸጋሁ፡ ለመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡...
                            </incipit>
                            </msItem>
                          <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.2">
                            <title>Miracle about the farmer who could not make a feast in honor of the Archangel because of drought and famine</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                              <locus from ="20r" to = "20v"/>ተአምሪሁ፡...ወሀሎ፡ ፩ብእሲ፡ መሃይምን፡ ወይሴፎ፡ ምሕረተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወይገብር፡ በዓሎ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ አመ፡ ፲ወ፪ለለኵሉ፡ አውራኅ፡ ወዝንቱ፡ ብእሲ፡ ኮነ፤ ይገብር፡ ማኅረስ፡...
                            </incipit>
                          </msItem>
                          <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.3">
                            <title>Greeting to the Archangel</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang = " gez">
                              <locus from = "20v"/>ሰላም፡ ለከ፡ ዓቃቤ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ እምተሀውኮ።
                            </incipit>
                          </msItem>
                          </msItem>

                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                       <locus from = "21r" to = "27r"/>
                       <title><foreign xml:lang = "gez">ያኅሥሥ:</foreign></title>
                       <note>(sic) ጥር፡ (added later in pencil)</note>

                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.1">
                         <title>Homily (by John, Bishop of Aksum), on the family of Dorotheos and Theopista</title>
                         <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                           <locus from ="21r" to = "26r"/>በስመ፡ አብ፡...እም፡ አመ፡ ፲ወ፪ለወርኃ፡ ታኅሣሥ፡...አሜን። ስምዑ፡ ኵልክሙ፡ አሕዛብ፡ ወአጽምዑ፡ ኵልክሙ፡ እለ፡ ትነብሩ፡ ውስተ፡ ዓለም፡...ወሀሎ፡ ፩ብእሲ፡ ዘርቱዕ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ዘስሙ፡ ዶራታዖስ፡ ወስመ፡ ብእሲቱ፡ ቴዎብስታ፡...
                         </incipit>
                       </msItem>
                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.2">
                         <title>Miracle on the farmer who neglected making the feast of the Archangel</title>
                         <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                           <locus from = "26r" to = "26v"/>ተአምሪሁ፡...ወሀሎ፡ ፩ብእሲ፡ ክርስቲያናዊ፡ ፈራሄ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወያፈቅሮ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ይነብር፡ በግብረ፡ ማኅረስ፡ ወዘርአ፡ ብዙኃ፡ ገራውሀ፡...
                         </incipit>
                       </msItem>
                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.3">
                         <title>Synaxary entry: Mission to save Jacob from the wrath of Esau</title>
                         <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                           <locus from = "26v" to = "27r"/>እስመ፡ በዛቲ፡ ዕለት፡ ፈነዎ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡...ኀበ፡ ያዕቆብ፡ እስራኤላዊ፡ አመ፡ አፍርሆ፡ ኤሳው፡ እኁሁ፡
                         </incipit>
                       </msItem>
                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.4">
                         <title>Greeting</title>
                         <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                           <locus from = "27r"/>ሰላም፡ ለከ፡ ሚካኤል፡ አሐዱ።
                         </incipit>
                       </msItem>
                     </msItem>

                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4">
                       <locus from = "27r" to = "32r"/>
                       <title>የካቲት፡</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                          <locus from = "27r" to = "30v"/>Homily (anonymous) on the man who prayed to the Archangel for his needs but bever worked, ወሀሎ፡ ፩ነዳይ፡ ውስተ፡ ውእቱ፡ ብሔር፡ ዓቢይ፡ ሃይማኖቱ፡ ወይስእል፡ መዓልተ፡ ወሌሊተ፡..., <locus from = "30v" to = "31v"/>Miracle, ተአምሪሁ፡...ወሀሎ፡ ፩ብእሲ፡ ዘይገብር፡ ምሕረተ፡ ለነዳያን፡ ወለምስኪናን፡ ወይገብር፡ ሠናየ፡ ለኵሉ፡ ሰብእ፡ ወሶበ፡ ርእየ፡ ጸላኤ፡ ሠናያት፡ ኂሩቶ፡..., Synaxary entry, <locus from = "32r"/>...ወበዛቲ፡ ዕለተ፡ ፈነዎ፡ ኀበ፡ ሶምሶን፡ ረዓታዊ፡ ወኢሎፍላዊ፡..., Greeting, <locus from = "32r"/>ሰላም፡ እብል፡ ዚያከ፡ ናዛዜ።
                        </incipit>
                     </msItem>
                   </msItem>



